snippet.title: Desktoptale - UNDEREVENT 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Desktoptale is a small program that puts a fully controllable Undertale, Undertale Yellow or Deltarune character of your choice on your Windows desktop! Visit the website for more information and downloads: https://desktoptale.toastworth.com/

For those who aren't aware, I've been working on this project since March of last year, although I'm pretty much done with it now. This trailer was first revealed in UNDEREVENT 2024 and I feel incredibly honored to have been a part of such an amazing project!
